            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><hr />\n<h2 id=\"2-the-mlp-baseline\">2. The MLP Baseline</h2>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">We train a simple MLP classifier that predicts each cell's next character\nbased on a local patch around it plus the action being taken.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Key insight:</strong> This model is strong on typing (local changes) but weaker on Enter\n(where distant cells change based on command semantics).</span></span>"
